    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior shows visible wear including scratches and minor dents on several panels. The interior has noticeable wear with some worn upholstery and minor damage to trim surfaces. The mechanical systems are functional but show signs of age and use. Overall, this is a usable vehicle that will require some attention.",
